So, to unban your console you'll need a special
utility. I only could find it

00:02:40.620 --> 00:02:46.400
for the very first CFW, which is 3.41. Perhaps
you would be luckier than me.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:49.810
Anyway, if you've been following the advice
I keep repeating like a freaking

00:02:49.810 --> 00:02:55.770
parrot - QA flag you console while you're
still on 3.55 - good for you, and

00:02:55.770 --> 00:03:00.989
you shouldn't have any trouble downgrading
to 3.41. If you didn't, well,

00:03:00.989 --> 00:03:04.360
downgrade we'll be harder for you, since first
you have to install a hybrid

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:10.160
CFW which tells it's a higher version, but
